# YB College Database (Yoobee Colleges)

## Description
This project is a command-line database system for YB College. It manages Students, Lecturers, Courses, and Classes.  
The system is built using **Python (sqlite3)** and follows an **EER-to-Relational Schema** mapping.

## Features
- Add, view, and delete students
- Add and view courses
- Easily extendable for lecturers and classes
- Uses SQLite3 (lightweight, file-based DB)

## Files
- database.py → Handles database creation
- manager.py → CRUD operations
- main.py → Command-line interface
- README.txt → Project documentation

## How to Run
```bash
python main.py
